NJ Div. of Fish and Wildlife Hunter Education Home Study Materials Hunter Education Home Study Course materials are available at the following vendors and Division offices. Please contact the vendor or Division office beforehand to confirm availability of Hunter Education materials and store/office hours. Print materials are available for download. The video is available on DVD and is also available online. To obtain the materials via US Priority Mail, send $5.60 IN US POSTAGE STAMPS ONLY, along with an index card with your name and address, to: The NJ Hunter Education Program offers two courses: FIRARMS and BOW; prior to 2014 there were separate Shotgun
